{
  "text": "Besides stability ratio, soil OM can be influenced by several soil properties. Soil OM showed a positive relationship with clay content (Table 3) . Clay particles can generate organic-mineral complexes, which results in an increased accumulation of organic matter. Thus, as clay content increases, both soil surface area and organic matter increase [CITATION_1] .",
